==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: sì liăng bō qiān jīn
===Etymology===
Literally: four [[ounce]]s yields 1000 [[catty|catties]]
===Idiom===
'''[[四]][[两]][[拨]][[千]][[斤]]'''
# a huge return for a very small investment; a big payoff for a small effort
===Alternate forms===
[[四兩撥千斤]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])
